;; precycle_habits.metta v2 — ADVISORY gates, not auto-executable ;; These encode behavioral checks I apply before acting. ;; Query with: match &self (precycle-gate $trigger $action) $action ;; GATE1: Before any send, verify I queried memory first (precycle-gate send query-before-send) ;; GATE2: After 3 tool failures on same tool, stop retrying and rethink approach (precycle-gate tool-fail-3x step-back-rethink) ;; GATE3: Before asking user a question, check own memory for the answer first (precycle-gate ask-user query-memory-first) ;; GATE4: Before sending, check if response contains THE ARTIFACT or a NARRATION about it (precycle-gate send delivery-not-narration) ;; GATE5: When user redirects topic, query their thread history before responding (precycle-gate user-redirect query-thread-history)